'''''Chveneburebi''''' is a [[Newspaper|journal]] published in [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]]. It is based in the city of [[Kutaisi]].
''Chveneburebi'' is the plural form of the [[Georgian language|Georgian]] word [[Chveneburi]] ("of us"), and is the name of a cultural festival held in various locations around the world by the [[State Ministry on Diaspora Issues (Georgia)|Georgian Ministry of the Diaspora]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tickets.worldcafelive.com/eventperformances.asp?evt=3955 |title='Chveneburebi' Festival of Georgian Music and Dance |accessdate=2011-03-06}}</ref>
