The '''√Üsaronenses''' or '''Aesaronenses''' were an ancient people of [[Sardinia]], noted by [[Ptolemy]] (III, 3).  They dwelt south of the [[Salcitani]] and the [[Lucuidonenses]] and north of the [[√Üchilenenses]] or Cornenses.

